property_details:
Very spacious 2 bedroom all Ensuite apartment for rent in nyali, ample parking Upto 3 cars, free water and good quality security. Rent inclusive of service charge 
Terms of payment;
1 deposit and 3 months rent

• Four Spacious bedrooms, three ensuite. 
• Master bedroom with a spacious balcony offering scenic views; 
• Modern open kitchen with pantry and wash area; 
• Spacious living room with dining area;
• Guest cloakroom
• Swimming Pool and gym at the roof top;
• 2 high speed lifts. 
• Two parking slots
• NWSC water together with borehole
• Standby generator and solar water heater;
• Apartment let out as unfurnished. 
• Located within Batubatu Gardens, a gated community between 1st and 2nd Parklands.
• Available from 1st August 2025.
